('10da132e-60c8-41b3-b926-5c3f6bdb622f', 'File', 'ফাইল', '', '', 'https://ggwpmrrtqocjcsnwqxze.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/cms-images/products/1771575834698.jpeg', '34a7db51-39be-450f-95e7-093f1efe00c8', 'file', 14, true, '2026-02-20 08:24:00.96997+00', '2026-03-12 05:39:27.594534+00'),
('ddb2a550-657f-469a-b408-14f4e5f9835e', 'Formal Solid Color Slim Neck Tie', 'ফর্মাল সলিড কালার স্লিম নেক টাই', 'Elegant solid color slim neck tie, 6cm width. Classic plain tie design that matches easily with any shirt or suit. Perfect for formal occasions, corporate events, and professional settings.', 'মার্জিত সলিড কালার স্লিম নেক টাই, ৬ সেমি প্রশস্ত। যেকোনো শার্ট বা স্যুটের সাথে সহজে মিলে যায়। আনুষ্ঠানিক অনুষ্ঠান, কর্পোরেট ইভেন্ট এবং পেশাদার পরিবেশের জন্য আদর্শ।', 'https://ggwpmrrtqocjcsnwqxze.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/cms-images/products-nobg/ties-collection.png', '9f96b5e4-f162-4590-b674-63cd42fc68c7', 'formal-solid-color-slim-neck-tie', 15, true, '2026-02-24 04:01:07.192288+00', '2026-02-24 04:06:05.014466+00'),
('949bc0d0-b0f8-4bc7-957a-4cf21447b944', 'Office Bag', '', 'premium high quality leather bag', 'প্রিমিয়াম উচ্চ মানের চামড়ার ব্যাগ', 'https://ggwpmrrtqocjcsnwqxze.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/cms-images/products/1773725226595.jpg', '99a19d25-6859-468f-bad5-958aa2ebdebf', 'Office Bag 001', 25, true, '2026-03-17 05:32:23.108436+00', '2026-03-17 05:54:53.221699+00'),
('ce96c937-741c-4e05-8d28-a9c5cd04e0d1', 'Make-Up Items For Gifting', 'মেকআপ গিফট আইটেম', 'A perfect gift combination of make-up items to surprise your loved one on any occasion. Includes La Femme Makeup Studio Deluxe Eyeshadows, Wet N Wild MegaGlo and more.', '', '/temp/corporate-makeup-gift.jpg', '9f96b5e4-f162-4590-b674-63cd42fc68c7', NULL, 100, true, '2026-02-24 05:22:14.23771+00', '2026-02-24 05:22:14.23771+00'),
('96788d20-5d19-4866-a9ad-3ace90df1a67', 'Unique Gift For Him', 'তার জন্য অনন্য উপহার', 'A perfect gift combination of essential items to wish your father, friends, colleague, brother at any occasion in Bangladesh. Includes Power Bank and other premium items.', '', '/temp/corporate-gift-him.jpg', '9f96b5e4-f162-4590-b674-63cd42fc68c7', NULL, 101, true, '2026-02-24 05:22:14.23771+00', '2026-02-24 05:22:14.23771+00'),
('155c6891-0356-413a-9904-b64a4e777859', 'Snake Plant In Ceramic Pot With Logo', 'লোগো সহ সিরামিক পটে স্নেক প্ল্যান্ট', 'Indoor snake plant in a branded ceramic pot with your company logo. Plants add beauty to office decor and are a great source of oxygen. Perfect for corporate gifting.', '', '/temp/corporate-snake-plant.jpg', '9f96b5e4-f162-4590-b674-63cd42fc68c7', NULL, 102, true, '2026-02-24 05:22:14.23771+00', '2026-02-24 05:22:14.23771+00'),
('f785c72a-c3be-4716-ae1d-4f04eed9fdad', 'Corporate Gift Package', 'কর্পোরেট গিফট প্যাকেজ', 'A wonderful assorted corporate happiness package that will surely make your employees happy. Customizable contents available for bulk orders.', '', '/temp/corporate-gift-package.jpg', '9f96b5e4-f162-4590-b674-63cd42fc68c7', NULL, 103, true, '2026-02-24 05:22:14.23771+00', '2026-02-24 05:22:14.23771+00'),
('d9334a34-79c7-43c4-964a-fb0ecae0d550', 'Corporate Customize Products Package', 'কর্পোরেট কাস্টমাইজ প্রোডাক্ট প্যাকেজ', 'Perfect gift package for celebrating corporate events. Customizable contents including branded items and premium snacks.', '', '/temp/corporate-customize-package.jpg', '9f96b5e4-f162-4590-b674-63cd42fc68c7', NULL, 105, true, '2026-02-24 05:22:14.23771+00', '2026-02-24 05:22:14.23771+00'),
('b4920fca-53d6-4c2b-9040-b27d5781e91f', 'Package For A New Beginning', 'নতুন শুরুর প্যাকেজ', 'Give it a fresh start with premium chocolates: Raffaello, Rocher, Truffle, Kit Kat, Dairy Milk Silk, Toblerone and more. Perfect for welcoming new employees or celebrating milestones.', '', '/temp/corporate-new-beginning.jpg', '9f96b5e4-f162-4590-b674-63cd42fc68c7', NULL, 106, true, '2026-02-24 05:22:14.23771+00', '2026-02-24 05:22:14.23771+00'),
('e31e70cc-ba12-4a0a-b96a-6fb29ea5c7ac', 'Gift Hamper With Tea & Celebration Drink', 'চা ও সেলিব্রেশন ড্রিংক গিফট হ্যাম্পার', 'Make your corporate people happy with this refreshing gift box. Includes Kazi & Kazi Orthodox Black Tea, Green Lemongrass Tea, and more premium beverages.', '', '/temp/corporate-tea-hamper.jpg', '9f96b5e4-f162-4590-b674-63cd42fc68c7', NULL, 107, true, '2026-02-24 05:22:14.23771+00', '2026-02-24 05:22:14.23771+00'),
('94dc57d5-7376-4244-a2f7-00ef2909c64c', 'Indoor Plant In Ceramic Mug With Logo', 'লোগো সহ সিরামিক মগে ইনডোর প্ল্যান্ট', 'Indoor plants in a branded ceramic mug with your company logo. Great for office decoration, adds beauty and fresh oxygen to workspace.', '', '/temp/corporate-indoor-plant.jpg', '9f96b5e4-f162-4590-b674-63cd42fc68c7', NULL, 108, true, '2026-02-24 05:22:14.23771+00', '2026-02-24 05:22:14.23771+00'),
('6f093189-c276-42b0-9a24-ea3f8f5b02c0', 'Gift For Diabetic Person', 'ডায়াবেটিক ব্যক্তির জন্য উপহার', 'A thoughtful gift package specially curated for diabetic colleagues and clients. Celebrate birthdays and office events with health-conscious gifting.', '', '/temp/corporate-diabetic-gift.jpg', '9f96b5e4-f162-4590-b674-63cd42fc68c7', NULL, 109, true, '2026-02-24 05:22:14.23771+00', '2026-02-24 05:22:14.23771+00')
